description: The legendary Sheila Jordan surprises vocalist Paul Marinaro by calling him up to the stage to improvise with her.  Green Mill, Chicago.  April 21, 2018
title: "Workshop Blues"  Sheila Jordan with Paul Marinaro
fulltitle: "Workshop Blues"  Sheila Jordan with Paul Marinaro
